║ §32 — GRAMMAR STRATIFICATION — S0–S3 for Safety & Adoption ║
║ Grounded in: CRANE (2025, constrained LLM generation); ║
║ GrammarCoder (Liang 2025, arXiv:2503.05507); ║
║ ANTHILL (Shevchenko 2026, progressive formalization) ║
