├── seedvm/
│   ├── Cargo.toml
│   └── src/
│       ├── lib.rs             ← `run_file()`, `run_bytes()`
│       ├── main.rs            ← `seedvm` CLI (run, trace, prove)
│       ├── value.rs           ← runtime Value enum
│       ├── state.rs           ← VMState, VmError, ProvenanceEvent
│       ├── executor.rs        ← bytecode interpreter (50+ opcodes)
