### SSA Control‑Flow Graph for a Conditional Agent

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    subgraph BLK0["Block 0 — ENTRY (dominates all)"]
        direction LR
        I0["Const 10 → local[0]"]
        I1["Const 5"]
        I2["LoadLocal 0"]
        I3["Gt (cmp: local[0] > 5)"]
        T0["BRANCH cond → then:BLK1, else:BLK2"]
    end

    BLK0 -->|"true (x > 5)"| BLK1
